Seen swimming amongst bubbles as the allover print of this mini backpack, Ponyo also appears as a super cute sleepy graphic on the removable front pocket. With gold-toned hardware, top handle, included crossbody strap (to attach to the front pocket for a new style!), brand badge, adjustable shoulder straps, and an interior floral lining, this set is all you need to bring the charming world of Ponyo to your next outing. Rock the look as one or split it into two, the choice is yours when you add this set to your accessory collection. A BoxLunch Exclusive!
